messages.messageBody:
Wow. I went to look at photos and there are several new ones. People have
swimming pools! Beaches! Beautiful art, interesting houses, bright-eyed
kids, this is great!

And Ren has a good-looking husband!

Some of you look really young. I personally am Very Old, but having a ten
year old keeps me relatively alert for my age. 8-)

Sandra
